,\"description\":\"Pet parents in the area rave about A Ruff Joint.  What makes this dog facility special is its clean, friendly, caring. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. they always make my dog so pretty and clean smelling on her grooming day This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (865) 661-5313. \",\"slug\":\"a-ruff-joint\",\"address\":\"3625 Fairmont Blvd\",\"street\":\"3625 Fairmont Blvd\",\"city\":\"Knoxville\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37917\",\"full_address\":\"3625 Fairmont Blvd, Knoxville, TN 37917, USA\",\"latitude\":36.01686479999999,\"longitude\":-83.9020511,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJlysxMHcWXIgR-p4wVDfsC8M\",\"phone\":\"(865) 661-5313\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.5,\"reviewCount\":71,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"8:30 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"8:30 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"8:30 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"8:30 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"8:30 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"Closed\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJMad9RAkvXIgRwq3wcN2GuuA\",\"name\":\"Adorable Pets Grooming\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Adorable Pets Grooming has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this dog facility special is its great, fantastic. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. she has groomed our dogs for years and is always been fantastic This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (865) 691-9236. Visit their website at https://m.facebook.com/Apgrooming/ to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"adorable-pets-grooming\",\"address\":\"10420 Kingston Pike # D3\",\"street\":\"10420 Kingston Pike # D3\",\"city\":\"Knoxville\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37922\",\"full_address\":\"10420 Kingston Pike # D3, Knoxville, TN 37922, USA\",\"latitude\":35.8978194,\"longitude\":-84.1285881,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJMad9RAkvXIgRwq3wcN2GuuA\",\"phone\":\"(865) 691-9236\",\"website\":\"https://m.facebook.com/Apgrooming/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.3,\"reviewCount\":64,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"8:00 AM – 4:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:00 AM – 3:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJn-yx2CQRXIgR2jNqMgRL93E\",\"name\":\"Agility Center of East Tennessee\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Agility Center of East Tennessee is a beloved dog facility in the area that consistently earns praise from pet owners.  What makes this dog facility special is its great. The staff's dedication to creating a positive experience for both dogs and their owners is evident in every visit. sylvie has always given us great feedback in what we do great and where we can improve This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (865) 523-7